    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ、はぁ……あ、葵！　良かった、やっと見つけた\n随分探したんだからな……はぁ",
      "startTime": 7.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-out-single-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_01-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "……あれ、{user}君？　どうしたのさ\nそんなに息切れして、運動不足なんじゃないの",
      "startTime": 14.1487725413,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "そりゃ、葵よりは運動不足かもしれないけど……\n……じゃなくて、葵を呼びに来たんだよ",
      "startTime": 22.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "撮影中にふらっといなくなって慌ててたら\n莉央さんが、この公園にいるかもって教えてくれたんだ",
      "startTime": 28.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_01-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "だって、いきなり機材トラブルだって言うしさ\n復旧するまで、ただ待ってるのも暇だし",
      "startTime": 35.5047160465,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_01-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "で、近くに公園があったのを思い出して\n久々にここで踊るのも悪くないかなって",
      "startTime": 41.5047160465,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "葵らしいな……でも、故障はなんとかなったらしい\n撮影も再開するから、ロケ場所に戻ろう",
      "startTime": 49.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_01-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "ねえ、もう少し休憩時間延びない？\nこんな短い時間じゃ、踊った気がしないよ",
      "startTime": 57.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "撮影が終わったらいくらでも踊れるだろ？\nそれに、今日はそうもいかないよ",
      "startTime": 64.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "『LizNoir・BIG4までの軌跡』の撮影なんだ\n初期メンバーの葵がいないと始まらない",
      "startTime": 71.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_01-aoi005.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……分かったよ。莉央にガミガミ言われたくないし\nこころと愛の前で、僕があんまりルーズなのもね",
      "startTime": 79.248570442,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "それにしても、莉央さんもよくこの公園が分かったな",
      "startTime": 82.731449731,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_01-aoi006.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、ここからバンプロのオフィスは近いからね\nデビューした頃は、よくここで気晴らしに踊ってたんだ",
      "startTime": 91.7019488969,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_01-aoi007.m4a",
      "text": "莉央は、最初の頃は知らなかったんだけどね\n昔、大喧嘩した時に、この公園を知られちゃって",
      "startTime": 99.3686155635,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_01-aoi008.m4a",
      "text": "僕が踊ってたら、すぐ連れ戻しに来るようになったんだ\nまったく、酷いと思わない？",
      "startTime": 107.4686155635,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さんも昔から苦労してたんだな……",
      "startTime": 109.7109277407,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_01-aoi009.m4a",
      "text": "ん？　苦労っていうのは、どういう意味？\nまるで僕が悪いみたいだね",
      "startTime": 117.5070281186,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_message-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3059.638548099997,
          "startTime": 120.5666666667
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5859.638548099994,
          "startTime": 123.3666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "いや、そういう訳じゃ……あ、スタジオから連絡だ\n十五分後に撮影再開らしい、急いで戻ろう",
      "startTime": 124.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_01-aoi010.m4a",
      "text": "……お、まだ機材のチェック中みたいだ\nこれなら、ギリギリ遅刻せずにすんだかな？",
      "startTime": 134.7512922444,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 130.4666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "shj",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_01-shj001.m4a",
      "text": "遅れちゃいないが、みんな葵を心配してたんだ\nまったく、撮影の時まで踊りに行くなんてな",
      "startTime": 142.5512922444,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_01-aoi011.m4a",
      "text": "三枝さんじゃないか、めずらしい\nいつも会議会議で、現場に来る暇なんかなさそうなのに",
      "startTime": 151.6512922444,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "shj",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_01-shj002.m4a",
      "text": "リズノワ結成当時の話もするって言うなら\n俺だって、時間くらい作るさ",
      "startTime": 159.2263809601,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_01-aoi012.m4a",
      "text": "よく言うよ。僕と莉央を組ませるだけ組ませて\n自分はさっさといなくなっちゃったじゃないか",
      "startTime": 166.1846255777,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_01-aoi013.m4a",
      "text": "あの後、こっちは大変だったんだよ\n主に莉央がだけど",
      "startTime": 171.817958911,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "shj",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_01-shj003.m4a",
      "text": "……莉央にも同じことを言われたよ、耳が痛いな\nそういや俺も取材受けるんだが、さて何を話したもんか",
      "startTime": 178.6512922444,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_01-aoi014.m4a",
      "text": "僕をスカウトした時の話でいいんじゃない？\n小学生の僕に、いきなり声を掛けてきて……",
      "startTime": 188.9996331055,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "shj",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_01-shj004.m4a",
      "text": "なぁ、君。随分楽しそうに踊るんだな\nちょっと俺の話を聞いてくれないか？",
      "startTime": 199.6846062499,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_01-aoi015.m4a",
      "text": "おじさん誰……？\nもしかして、フシンシャってやつ？",
      "startTime": 205.8846062499,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "shj",
